  "keyFeatures": [
    "Weighted undirected graph built from JSON constellation data",
    "Dijkstra's algorithm for shortest-path traversal between stars",
    "DFS-based longest-path algorithm constrained by donkey resources",
    "Donkey entity with energy, health, grass, and age resource simulation",
    "Interactive Arcade GUI with graph visualization, status bars, and edge toggling",
    "Dynamic path blocking/unblocking via mouse click on graph edges",
    "Hypergiant star events that trigger teleportation and resource bonuses",
    "JSON-driven graph loading with file picker dialog",
    "Toast notifications and dialog prompts for in-game events",
    "Death-cause tracking with detailed post-mortem reporting"
  ],
